track_notes:
Good dirt road approach to YU/IS-022, on dry weather any high clearence car will do. Unfortunately, the road goes through Pasuljanske livade military shooting range, so sometimes it is closed to public.
If the road is closed, turn back and try the other track: YU/IS-022 via Prskalo waterfall.
Short walk through the woods to the summit. The summit is in a hunting reserve.
track_title: YU/IS-022 short walk from parked vehicle

track_notes:
Alternative 4x4 drive to YU/IS-022. There might be mud and rocks along the dirt road. Stop and visit Prskalo waterfall along the way.
This is a fragment of a track orginally published at http://www.stazeibogaze.info/2010/01/30/resavica-pasuljanske-livade-valkaluci-prskalo/
